
Russian enterprises in the spring of 2015: Reaction to monetary shock and activities in the context of the recession




 
© 2015, Pleiades Publishing, Ltd. The article analyzes and comments on the results of another overview of real sector enterprises carried out by Institute of Economic Forecasting of Russian Academy of Sciences. It contains data on the effect of the exchange rate of the ruble to the US dollar and the euro on Russian enterprises and states the causes of enterprises’ attention to the exchange rate and the effect of the monetary shock of December 2014 on the competition in the Russian internal market. It also contains information on the changes of investment activities and demand for labor of the enterprises in the context of the crisis of the Russian economy. The article presents the opinions of enterprises on the anti-crisis support of federal and regional authorities.


